        <Parent_String>inland vessels [300232913], watercraft by location or context [300232910], watercraft by operating environment [300232899], watercraft by specific type [300219289], watercraft [300042940], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
